These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
Pet: hedgehog, turtle, chinchilla, dog
1. Pet:turtle is on the left of Pet:hedgehog##1
2. Food:mango == Pet:dog##1
3. Pet:chinchilla is on the right of Pet:hedgehog##1
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Pet:dog##1
5. Food:raspberry is on the left of Pet:hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Pet   | turtle  | hedgehog     | chinchilla   | dog |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Color: light-blue, red, orange, black
Sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. Color:black == Sport:soccer##1
2. Color:light-blue is on the far right##1
3. Color:red is on the right of Color:black##1
4. Color:black is on the right of Sport:swimming##1
5. Sport:soccer is on the left of Sport:parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | orange | black | red | light-blue    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
Hobby: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling, writing
Pet: cat, ferret, guinea-pig, rabbit
1. Pet:guinea-pig is on the left of Pet:rabbit##1
2. Hobby:fishing == Pet:cat##1
3. Pet:ferret is on the far right##1
4. Pet:rabbit is on the right of Hobby:writing##1
5. Hobby:traveling is on the left of Pet:ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | fishing | writing | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| Pet   | cat   | guinea-pig | rabbit | ferret         |

